gobblin.writer.objectstore

Class ObjectStoreWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.instrumented.writer.InstrumentedDataWriter<ObjectStoreOperation>
      • gobblin.writer.objectstore.ObjectStoreWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Instrumentable, FinalState, DataWriter<ObjectStoreOperation>, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    @Alpha
public class ObjectStoreWriter
extends InstrumentedDataWriter<ObjectStoreOperation>
    A writer to execute operations on a object in any object store. The record type of this writer is an ObjectStoreOperation. The ObjectStoreOperation encapsulates operation specific metadata and actions.
